@node Main "Oslide - Documentation"

                              'Oslide' 1.3

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Oslide' is @{" played " link play} on an 11 by 11 tile board with an empty
space in the center. The idea is to move tiles so that 3 tiles of
the same pattern line up, either horizontally or vertically. When
3 tiles with the same pattern are lined up, their patterns are
removed making them empty tiles (but still moveable). The goal is
to clear all the tiles in the least amount of moves.

  ...Note that there is no time limit, so take your time!

  Have fun!

